---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
	title="About the studio"
	description="We shape product, brand, and code for mission-driven teams."
	eyebrow="Studio"
>
	<section class="content-shell py-12 space-y-8"> 
		<div class="space-y-3 max-w-3xl">
			<p class="m-0 text-ink text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight">Roller Coaster Tech Nerd</p>
			<p class="m-0 text-muted">
				I love exploring new technologies, solving problems, and creating systems of technologies that interact with each other. I love to dive into solving common problems through projects that can be fully software or even simply bodjing random components to create something new and build an ecosystem of interconnected technologies that are designed for the user. I have found an interest in the amusement industry and especially with the roller coasters that influences my work. I love their history, engineering design decisions, and of course the programming. I plan to continue my journey doing what I already love to do.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
